data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 2-story townhome with 3 bdrms & 2.5 baths. Nestled in a prime  location, this home has been meticulously updated, boasting a range of modern features that elevate  both its charm & energy efficiency. As you step inside, you'll notice the remodeled kitchen, featuring a sleek quartz countertop & brick backsplash. Energy-conscious upgrades are also a highlight of this property. In 2019, the attic insulation was increased & blown in, ensuring optimal temperature control & energy savings all year. The roof received a major makeover with a Title 24 compliant design, guaranteeing both durability & energy efficiency. The double pane Anderson windows installed in 2019 & 80-gallon hybrid electric water heater provide additional eco-friendly benefits. For all your  storage needs, the 2-car garage comes with approximately 200 sq ft of extra overhead space & wiring for an EV charging station for those who want to keep their electric vehicles ready to go. Ideally situated, this home offers easy access to dining & shopping at Loehmann's Plaza & The UV.  For fitness enthusiasts, the American River Bike Trail is one mile away & offers 30 + miles of paved trail. Don't miss the opportunity to own this incredible property in a prime location.
